title: Power Starz to Rap Starz
itunes:title: Power Starz to Rap Starz
description:
FRI 7/15 - The Breakfast Club is joined by Ghost, Tommy, Tasha & Angela from the cast of Starz' #1 hit show "POWER". Sorry, we fanned out...that would be Omari, Joseph, Naturi & Lela in real life. Then a powerful rap star out of Cali named Schoolboy Q sits down with us to break down his new album "BLANK FACE".
